        "created_at": "2016-01-30T15:55:13.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Miss selling these guys\u2026all the wines are great, and white or red all seem to age better than most of their peers.  Finally drank my 2003 David Lett Pinot South Block a couple years ago to commemorate his accomplishments and passing.  Never would have guessed 2003.</p>",
